---
import Section from '../layout/Section.astro';
---

<Section id="geneease" class="flex flex-col">
  <div id="geneease-canvas" class="absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-30 md:opacity-100 md:translate-x-1/4"></div>

  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-[1] bg-gradient-to-b from-black/40 via-transparent to-black/60 pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 pt-12 md:pt-16 lg:pt-20 text-center">
    <span class="hidden md:block text-sm text-white/50 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Featured Project</span>
    <img src="/assets/images/geneease-logo.svg" alt="GeneEase" class="h-10 mx-auto mb-4" />
    <p class="text-xl text-white/70">
      AI-Assisted Therapeutic Target Discovery
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 flex-1"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 pb-8">
    <div class="max-w-xl space-y-8">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">The Challenge</h3>
          <p class="text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
            <span class="gradient-text font-medium">Biomedical researchers</span> spend weeks manually querying scientific databases and calling bioinformatics tools, cross-referencing results across <a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-white hover:text-white/80 underline underline-offset-2 transition-colors">PubMed</a>, <a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/clinvar/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-white hover:text-white/80 underline underline-offset-2 transition-colors">ClinVar</a>, <a href="https://www.uniprot.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-white hover:text-white/80 underline underline-offset-2 transition-colors">UniProt</a>, and dozens more — then synthesizing findings into actionable insights.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-l-2 border-white/20 pl-6">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Our Solution</h3>
          <p class="text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
            <span class="gradient-text font-medium">ReAct AI agents</span> that reason through complex biomedical questions. The system autonomously orchestrates bioinformatics tools across 39M+ papers, 60K+ genes, and 28M+ proteins.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-l-2 border-white/20 pl-6">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Technology</h3>
          <p class="text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
            <span class="gradient-text font-medium">LangGraph</span> orchestrates stateful agent workflows powered by frontier LLMs. RAG pipelines with BioBERT embeddings enable hybrid search across patient documents.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="hidden md:grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 mt-8">
      <div class="feature-card flex gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white/40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path d="M19.5 14.25v-2.625a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375h-1.5A1.125 1.125 0 0113.5 7.125v-1.5a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375H8.25m0 12.75h7.5m-7.5 3H12M10.5 2.25H5.625c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v17.25c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125h12.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V11.25a9 9 0 00-9-9z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-white font-medium mb-1">23+ Bio Tools</h4>
          <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">
            PubMed, ClinVar, UniProt, STRING, and more. Unified API access to the world's biomedical knowledge bases.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card flex gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white/40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-white font-medium mb-1">90%+ Accuracy</h4>
          <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">
            Validated against expert annotations. Citations and evidence chains for every claim. Transparent reasoning paths.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card flex gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white/40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path d="M3.75 13.5l10.5-11.25L12 10.5h8.25L9.75 21.75 12 13.5H3.75z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-white font-medium mb-1">10x Faster</h4>
          <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">
            Hours instead of weeks. Parallel agent execution synthesizes findings across databases simultaneously.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 w-full text-center pb-6">
    <p class="text-white/40 text-xs">
      Research Platform · 2025
    </p>
  </div>
</Section>
